channel.title: Auto Rune is back!
channel.description:
Auto Rune, is now back online! http://Auto Rune.org (no spaces)
Auto Rune works for the current version of runescape classic, also has a hp highscores.. This highscores system has been generated by the bot with players in your local area and sends there hp to the google Database.. It's a very good add on for the rsc scene (Seeming as no highscores for real RSC)
This is a 100% working Runescape classic bot..
Hope you enjoy.
